data.description: Introducing a Spectacular 2-Story, 5 Bedroom, 3 Bath Home in the Heart of a Golf Course & Golf Cart Friendly Neighborhood!    5 Bedrooms - Spacious and Comfortable for the Whole Family!  3 Full Baths - No More Morning Rush Hours!  Bonus Living Room on the Second Floor - Perfect for Entertainment!  Open Kitchen Area with Walk-In Pantry- Ideal for Culinary Enthusiasts!  Fenced back yard   Golf Course Community - Golfers’ Haven      Smart Home Security Features:  Smart Code Locks - Enhanced Safety!    Community Amenities:  Clubhouse, Pools, Tennis, soccer fields, and Volleyball Courts.  Curbside Mail Delivery.    Stainless Steel Range, Microwave, and Dishwasher.    This is more than a new home; it's a new way of life. Envision yourself waking up to the sight of verdant fairways, playing a round of golf, and then unwinding in your gorgeous, high-tech, and environmentally friendly home.    Don't pass up the chance to settle into a life of luxury in a dynamic neighborhood. Get in touch with us right now to schedule a personal tour of this magnificent property.     Home is occupied. Appointments required!    #DreamHome #GolfCourseLiving #SmartHome #LuxuryRealEstate
